# 🤖 Smart AI LMS – AI Powered Learning Management System

Smart AI LMS is an intelligent learning platform that combines AI-powered assistance, course management, and automated quiz generation to enhance student learning experiences.

---

## 🚀 Key Features

### 📚 Course Management
- Add course videos using YouTube links
- Organize learning resources
- Easy content accessibility

### 🤖 AI Assistant
- Instant doubt clarification
- Course recommendations
- Personalized learning support

### 📝 AI Quiz Generator
- AI-generated quizzes
- Multiple subjects support
- Difficulty-based assessments
- Built-in timer

### 🔐 Authentication System
- Secure Login & Signup
- Student and Admin Roles
- User Management

---

## 🏗️ System Architecture

1. Authentication Module
2. Course Management Module
3. AI Assistant Engine
4. Quiz Generation System
5. Learning Dashboard

---

## 🛠️ Technology Stack

### 🎨 Frontend
- React.js
- JavaScript
- HTML5
- CSS3

### ⚙️ Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

### 🗄️ Database
- MongoDB

### 🧠 AI Integration
- Google Gemini API
- NLP-Based Quiz Generation

### ☁️ Deployment
- Vercel

---

## 📂 Project Modules

### 🏠 Home Page
Platform introduction and navigation.

### 📊 Dashboard
Course management and AI assistant access.

### 🤖 AI Assistant
Provides learning support and recommendations.

### 📝 AI Quiz
Generates quizzes dynamically based on selected topics.

### 🔑 Authentication
User registration and login functionality.

